attachments.title: Patch 1.0.3 Notes! - Pathfinder Adventures: Announcements and News
attachments.text: Page 1 of 2 - Patch 1.0.3 Notes! - posted in Pathfinder Adventures: Announcements and News: Hey there, everyone! Early next week well be releasing the next update for Pathfinder Adventures! Not only will this update include Adventure Deck 3, The Hook Mountain Massacre, but well also be addressing issues you have all found as well as issues weve come across while testing. Now without further ado, lets get this party started! NEW Looking for what will be new come pat...
attachments.fallback: Obsidian Forum Community: Patch 1.0.3 Notes! - Pathfinder Adventures: Announcements and News

text:
Adventure Deck 3, The Hook Mountain Massacre!
Character Roles! When you complete the final scenario of the adventure, you'll unlock role specializations for your characters. Will Merisiel become a Thief or an Acrobat? Will Kyra go down the path of an Exorcist or a Healer? The choice is yours!
5 new scenarios, including the game-changing "Here Comes the Flood!"
4 new locations!
4 new maps!
Over 40 new monsters, henchmen, and villains!
More weapons, spells, items, loot and more!
- Tier 3 Quest mode now available! A different take on the Pathfinder Adventure Card Game formula, take a group and level them up in adventures that are apart from story mode! Now with more ogres.
- Cloud saves: Characters and parties in story mode are now uploaded to the cloud for easy access across devices.
- UI Improvement: Summoned monsters are now marked as summons!
- UI Improvement: When opening treasure chests in the store, the decks that cards come from is more apparent.
- UI Improvement: A "Back" button is now present on the adventure screen when you first start a party.
